data.text:
Autocorrect is coming for your mind

How much of your word choice is yours vs Siri’s?

Anyone who’s even slightly computer literate and or owns it iPhone, or talks to someone who owns an iPhone for texting and uses swearwords knows about the tawdry practice of “ducking“.
